OL,3,CBlue badge fraud reported as drivers
OL,4,Ctry to dodge parking costs
OL,6,FCalls are being made for blue badge
OL,7,Fparking fraud to become as
OL,8,Funacceptable as drink driving after a
OL,9,FWest Country council said it had seen
OL,10,Fthe problem double in the last year.
OL,12,FThe permits are issued to people with
OL,13,Fhealth conditions and disabilities to
OL,14,Fpark vehicles in dedicated spaces,
OL,15,Foften for free.
OL,17,FNorth Somerset Council says it has
OL,18,Fconfiscated 547 badges since 2017 but
OL,19,Fthere's a rising issue with blue
OL,20,Fbadges being misused.
