OL,3,CBlue badge fraud reported as drivers
OL,4,Ctry to dodge parking costs
OL,6,FThis includes someone borrowing
OL,7,Fanother person's permit or using it
OL,8,Fafter it has expired, but there have
OL,9,Falso been cases where people have been
OL,10,Fusing fake or stolen badges.
OL,12,FNew figures from the RAC show reported
OL,13,Fcases of blue badge misuse have
OL,14,Fincreased nationally by 1,000% since
OL,15,F2016.
OL,17,FEven as ITV West Country was out with
OL,18,Fenforcement officers in Weston-super-
OL,19,FMare, they confronted a man alone in
OL,20,Fhis car using a permit that didn't
OL,21,Fbelong to him.
