OL,6,FHe says the clampdown checks he makes
OL,7,Fare important work: "To take a badge
OL,8,Fthat's been misused gives you a glow,
OL,9,Fbecause I regularly go to a Disability
OL,10,FAction Group and I see how our work
OL,11,Fmassively helps this group and others
OL,12,Fwho are genuine badge holders and
OL,13,Fgenuinely need the space.
OL,15,F"If someone's parked in there, it can
OL,16,Fmean they can't do the event, they
OL,17,Fcan't go to the shop they needed to
OL,18,Fget to. It's just not fair."
